@startuml Before and After Architecture
!theme plain
title Code Cleanup Transformation: v1.0 → v2.0\nFrom Monolithic to Modular

package "BEFORE (v1.0-pre-cleanup)" {
  component "task_motor.c\n1,380 lines" as OldTaskMotor #pink {
    [God Object]
    [Mixed Concerns]
    [Protocol Parsing]
    [Motor Control]
    [Spindle Hold Logic]
    [Jam Detection]
    [Temperature Monitoring]
    [Initialization Code]
    [Status Query Logic]
  }

  component "motor.c\n1,116 lines" as OldMotor #pink {
    [Motor API]
    [Protocol Building]
    [Duplicate Parsing]
    [Magic Numbers]
  }

  note right of OldTaskMotor
    **Problems:**
    • 8+ infinite UART loops (CRITICAL)
    • 321-line motor_query_status()
    • Protocol duplicated 3 times
    • Spindle hold inline (115 lines)
    • Jam detection inline (30 lines)
    • Temp monitoring inline (55 lines)
    • 20+ magic numbers
    • No error handling on UART
    • No diagnostics
    • No unit tests
    • Thread safety undocumented
  end note
}

package "AFTER (v2.0-complete)" {

  component "task_motor.c\n1,207 lines\n(-12.5%)" as NewTaskMotor #lightgreen {
    [Task Orchestration]
    [State Machine]
    [Event Processing]
    [Init Helpers] #lightblue
  }

  component "motor.c\n1,038 lines\n(-7%)" as NewMotor #lightgreen {
    [Motor Control API]
    [MCB Communication]
  }

  component "motor_protocol.c\n208 lines\nPhase 6" as NewProtocol #yellow {
    [Protocol Layer]
    [16 unit tests ✅]
  }

  component "diagnostics.c\n320 lines\nPhase 7" as NewDiag #yellow {
    [Error Tracking]
    [Performance Metrics]
    [STATS/ERRORS/PERF]
  }

  component "spindle_hold.c\n150 lines\nPhase 2.1" as NewHold #cyan {
    [Position Lock]
  }

  component "jam.c\n282 lines\nPhase 2.3" as NewJam #cyan {
    [Safety Monitoring]
  }

  component "temperature.c\n164 lines\nPhase 2.2" as NewTemp #cyan {
    [Thermal Monitoring]
  }

  component "utilities.c\n25 lines\nPhase 3.3" as NewUtils #lightgray {
    [Common Helpers]
    [7 unit tests ✅]
  }

  NewTaskMotor --> NewMotor
  NewTaskMotor --> NewProtocol
  NewTaskMotor --> NewHold
  NewTaskMotor --> NewJam
  NewTaskMotor --> NewTemp
  NewTaskMotor --> NewDiag

  NewMotor --> NewProtocol
  NewMotor --> NewUtils

  NewProtocol --> NewUtils
  NewHold --> NewMotor
}

note as Stats
  **Transformation Metrics**

  **Code Size:**
  • Combined: 2,496 → 2,245 lines (-10.1%)
  • task_motor.c: 1,380 → 1,207 (-12.5%)
  • motor.c: 1,116 → 1,038 (-7.0%)

  **Modules:**
  • Before: 2 monolithic files
  • After: 7 organized modules

  **Safety:**
  • Infinite loops: 8+ → 0 (100% fixed)
  • UART timeouts: None → All protected
  • Error handling: None → Comprehensive

  **Quality:**
  • Magic numbers: 20+ → 0 (13 constants)
  • Unit tests: 0 → 23 (100% passing)
  • Diagnostics: None → Full system
  • Thread safety: Undocumented → Classified

  **Development:**
  • Git commits: 24 atomic commits
  • Git tags: 11 rollback points
  • Documentation: 4 technical reports
  • Test coverage: Core modules tested
end note

note as Features
  **New Capabilities in v2.0:**

  ✅ Cannot hang (Phase 1)
  ✅ Real-time diagnostics (Phase 7)
  ✅ Hardware failsafe (Phase 1.1b)
  ✅ Queue monitoring (Phase 5.3)
  ✅ Unit tested protocol (Phase 9)
  ✅ Modular architecture (Phases 2,6,8)
  ✅ Comprehensive logging (Phase 1)
  ✅ Thread-safe (Phase 5)
end note

@enduml
